OL,4,Crates increase of more than 5%
OL,6,FBelfast City Council has agreed an
OL,7,Fincrease in the district rate of more
OL,8,Fthan 5%.JTina Black, chair of the
OL,9,Fcouncil's Strategic Policy and
OL,10,FResources Committee, said the 5.44%
OL,11,Fincrease for residents would "support
OL,12,Four council workers with fair pay and
OL,13,Falso invest in improvements which will
OL,14,Fmake a real difference to citizens".
OL,15,FThe council said the rates rise means
OL,16,Fan average weekly increase of 35p for
OL,17,Fa terraced property, 53p for a three-
OL,18,Fbedroom semi-detached property, #1.18
OL,19,Ffor a four-bedroom detached property,
OL,20,F34p for an apartment, #8.94 for an
OL,21,Foffice property and #7.32 for a retail
OL,22,Fproperty.
